How It Works Query Flow 1. User asks: “How do I sort a list in Python?” ↓ 2. ShardManager detects: - Language: python - Topic: algorithm (sorting) ↓ 3. Auto-loads relevant shards: - core/algorithms - languages/python ↓ 4. Searches only those shards ↓ 5. Returns answer with sources

Memory Management · Core shards stay in memory while chat is active · Language/Framework shards load on demand, expire after TTL · Project shards load when working on that project · LRU eviction when max shards reached

